OL,3,CThousands lose NHS healthcare funding
OL,4,Cafter living 'longer than expected'
OL,6,FThousands of people are having NHS
OL,7,Ffunding for their care withdrawn after
OL,8,Fliving longer than expected, new
OL,9,Fresearch suggests.
OL,11,FPeople given fast-track NHS Continuing
OL,12,FHealthcare (CHC) to provide support at
OL,13,Fthe end of their lives can have it
OL,14,Fremoved following a review, leaving
OL,15,Fthem needing to find the money for
OL,16,Ftheir own care.
