OL,3,CThousands lose NHS healthcare funding
OL,4,Cafter living 'longer than expected'
OL,6,FA report from Age UK found huge
OL,7,Fvariation in who can access CHC, even
OL,8,Ffor longer-term conditions, with 58%
OL,9,Fof adults who applied getting support
OL,10,Fin some parts of England, dropping to
OL,11,F5% in other regions.
OL,13,FThe charity warned that families find
OL,14,Fthe system "a complete con", with
OL,15,Fdecisions being made on an "ad hoc"
OL,16,Fbasis and happening "behind closed
OL,17,Fdoors".
OL,19,FCHC is a package of care funded solely
OL,20,Fby the NHS when people are determined
OL,21,Fto have a "primary health need".
