OL,3,CThousands lose NHS healthcare funding
OL,4,Cafter living 'longer than expected'
OL,6,FTerminally ill or rapidly declining
OL,7,Fpatients are given fast-track CHC,
OL,8,Fwhile others are given standard CHC if
OL,9,Fthey are expected to live longer and
OL,10,Fhave ongoing needs.
OL,12,FEligibility for funding is decided
OL,13,Flocally by teams who report into
OL,14,FIntegrated Care Boards (ICBs), with
OL,15,Fassessors deciding whether people's
OL,16,Fneeds are high enough to qualify for
OL,17,Ffunding.
