OL,3,CThousands lose NHS healthcare funding
OL,4,Cafter living 'longer than expected'
OL,6,FAccording to Age UK, while the number
OL,7,Fof people deemed eligible for CHC has
OL,8,Frisen, the increase is made up of new
OL,9,Ffast-track patients who are only
OL,10,Fexpected to receive the funding for a
OL,11,Fshort time.
OL,13,FPA news agency analysis of NHS data
OL,14,Fshows the number of people deemed
OL,15,Feligible for the standard, longer-term
OL,16,FCHC funding has fallen 37% since 2018.
OL,18,FFor the 12-month period to the end of
OL,19,FSeptember 2024, some 10,538
OL,20,Fassessments resulted in people being
OL,21,Fdeemed eligible for CHC.
