OL,3,CThousands lose NHS healthcare funding
OL,4,Cafter living 'longer than expected'
OL,6,FThis is down from 16,599 for the 12
OL,7,Fmonths to the end of September 2018.
OL,9,FIn addition, Freedom of Information
OL,10,Fsnapshot data gathered by PA from ICBs
OL,11,Faround England suggests thousands of
OL,12,Fpeople are having fast-track funding
OL,13,Fremoved, with experts saying this is
OL,14,Fbecause they are living longer than
OL,15,Fexpected, even though their needs may
OL,16,Fnot have not changed.
OL,18,FFor example, the FOI revealed that, in
OL,19,FCounty Durham, from July 2022 to
OL,20,FDecember 2023, some 2,662 fast-track
OL,21,FCHC funding allocations were reviewed.
