OL,11,FIn South Yorkshire, from the 2021/22
OL,12,Ffinancial year to February this year,
OL,13,F581 people had fast-track funding
OL,14,Freviewed, of whom 343 were deemed no
OL,15,Flonger eligible and 229 remained
OL,16,Feligible for funding. Others were
OL,17,Fgiven NHS funded nursing care at the
OL,18,Flower rate.
