OL,3,CThousands lose NHS healthcare funding
OL,4,Cafter living 'longer than expected'
OL,6,FAge UK said that many older people
OL,7,Fwith chronic ill health and
OL,8,Fsignificant care needs are wrongly
OL,9,Fmissing out on CHC funding, leaving
OL,10,Fsome with huge care bills.
OL,12,FIts report said: "The data, and
OL,13,Faccounts of older people that feature
OL,14,Fin this report, suggest that CHC as a
OL,15,Flong-term intervention to support
OL,16,Fpeople with complex needs to live well
OL,17,Fis becoming less available.
