OL,3,CThousands lose NHS healthcare funding
OL,4,Cafter living 'longer than expected'
OL,6,F"There is also evidence that suggests
OL,7,Fthat those that do receive fast-track
OL,8,FCHC are increasingly losing
OL,9,Feligibility at review."
OL,11,FThe report said that, in theory,
OL,12,Feligibility decisions should be
OL,13,Findependent of budgetary constraints,
OL,14,Fwhile finance officers should not be
OL,15,Fpart of a decision-making process on
OL,16,Fwho gets funding.
OL,18,FHowever, it said that in practice ICBs
OL,19,Fhave been under pressure to make
OL,20,Fsavings from their CHC budgets for
OL,21,Fseveral years.
