OL,6,FCaroline Abrahams, charity director
OL,7,Ffor Age UK, said there was clear
OL,8,Fevidence of NHS "rationing", adding:
OL,9,F"It's no exaggeration to say that many
OL,10,Ffamilies come to view Continuing
OL,11,FHealthcare funding as a complete con,
OL,12,Fand the data suggest the gap between
OL,13,Fwhat it is supposed to do and what it
OL,14,Fis actually doing is growing.
