OL,3,CThousands lose NHS healthcare funding
OL,4,Cafter living 'longer than expected'
OL,6,F"It is deeply unfair to expose
OL,7,Ffamilies dealing with the serious ill
OL,8,Fhealth of a loved one to further
OL,9,Ftrauma by making them battle for money
OL,10,Fin an opaque system, where decision-
OL,11,Fmaking seems pretty ad hoc and happens
OL,12,Fbehind closed doors.
OL,14,F"It's also a recipe for deepening
OL,15,Finequalities, since more advantaged
OL,16,Ffamilies are much better able to fight
OL,17,Ffor their rights than others.
