OL,3,CThousands lose NHS healthcare funding
OL,4,Cafter living 'longer than expected'
OL,6,F"In addition, the extreme postcode
OL,7,Flottery for CHC makes a mockery of the
OL,8,Fidea that this is a rules-based system
OL,9,Fwhich is not influenced by the state
OL,10,Fof local NHS finances. It plainly is."
OL,12,FMs Abrahams said there have been "long-
OL,13,Fstanding gripes" about people being
OL,14,Funfairly barred from receiving CHC
OL,15,Ffunding because the eligibility
OL,16,Fprocess is rigged against them.
