OL,3,CThousands lose NHS healthcare funding
OL,4,Cafter living 'longer than expected'
OL,6,FShe said that any funding that is
OL,7,Favailable now seems to be moving away
OL,8,Ffrom being a source of longer-term
OL,9,Fcare funding for "profoundly frail and
OL,10,Funwell older people, to one focused
OL,11,Fmore and more on short, sharp
OL,12,Finjections of cash to support those at
OL,13,Fthe end of life".
OL,15,FShe added: "This is to the extent that
OL,16,Fif a person does not die as quickly as
OL,17,Fexpected, they are at increasing risk
OL,18,Fof having their CHC funding taken
OL,19,Faway."
