OL,6,FMarie Curie executive director of
OL,7,Fpolicy and research, Dr Sam Royston,
OL,8,Fsaid that to "hear people are being
OL,9,Fstopped from receiving the support
OL,10,Fthey so desperately need is appalling".
OL,12,FHe added: "We are well aware of the
OL,13,Fstrain on the health system, and
OL,14,Fwithdrawing this funding runs contrary
OL,15,Fto enabling people to have care in the
OL,16,Fcommunity, rather than ending up in
OL,17,Femergency departments and hospital
OL,18,Fbeds, which is often not the place
OL,19,Fwhere they want to die.
