OL,6,F"It's disappointing to hear that we
OL,7,Fare in such a place in 2024, and
OL,8,Fdiscussions must now happen at pace
OL,9,Fabout a sustainable, long-term
OL,10,Fsolution for funding CHC for dying
OL,11,Fpeople."
OL,13,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "Eligibility
OL,14,Ffor NHS continuing healthcare funding
OL,15,Fis determined on an individual basis
OL,16,Fby local health and social care
OL,17,Fprofessionals in line with guidance
OL,18,Fand regulations set by the Department
OL,19,Fof Health and Social Care.
